405
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:24,870
Choď preč!

406
00:39:24,888 --> 00:39:26,100
Qi Luo!

407
00:39:28,100 --> 00:39:30,200
To je pre tvoje dobro,
prečo to nechápeš?

408
00:39:30,388 --> 00:39:31,888
Qi Luo...

409
00:39:40,900 --> 00:39:42,900
Ty si moja najdrahšia...

410
00:39:43,388 --> 00:39:45,500
Nikto mi ťa nemôže ukradnúť!

411
00:40:22,888 --> 00:40:23,488
Ling...!

412
00:40:24,388 --> 00:40:25,388
Qi Luo...!

413
00:40:25,888 --> 00:40:28,880
Čo sa stalo?

414
00:40:32,700 --> 00:40:35,580
Sľúbil, že už mi to nikdy neurobí!

415
00:40:35,888 --> 00:40:38,880
Prisahal, že nie!

416
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:44,000
Nenávidím ho!

417
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:45,850
Na smrť ho nenávidím!

418
00:40:45,888 --> 00:40:47,300
Qi Luo...

419
00:40:47,388 --> 00:40:48,870
Nenávidím ho!

420
00:40:48,888 --> 00:40:51,380
Upokoj sa...upokoj sa...

421
00:40:58,388 --> 00:41:00,000
Teraz som len chcela...

422
00:41:00,388 --> 00:41:02,580
všetko, čo som chcela, aby zmizol.

423
00:41:04,388 --> 00:41:07,000
Kompletne a nadobro
zmizol z tohto sveta.

424
00:41:09,388 --> 00:41:11,600
Keď som si konečne uvedomila, čo robím,

425
00:41:12,388 --> 00:41:14,888
bol už celý pokrytý krvou,

426
00:41:14,889 --> 00:41:16,389
ležal na zemi

427
00:41:25,388 --> 00:41:27,580
Si si istá, že je mŕtvy?

428
00:41:28,388 --> 00:41:29,780
Stále som naňho volala

429
00:41:29,888 --> 00:41:31,888
znova a znova

430
00:41:32,888 --> 00:41:34,880
ale ani sa nepohol!

431
00:41:35,500 --> 00:41:37,800
Musí byť mŕtvy!

