Haló?

435
00:42:08,888 --> 00:42:09,388
Qi Luo?

436
00:42:11,388 --> 00:42:14,388
Mama... Mama, nechcela som to!

437
00:42:14,580 --> 00:42:17,380
To preto, že sa ku mne rozbehol a...

438
00:42:18,180 --> 00:42:20,200
Ja viem.

439
00:42:20,388 --> 00:42:22,000
Tvoj otec mi to už povedal.

